[Cellular regulation of the lower urinary tract as a cause of the bladder 
overactivity and reduced efficiency of pharmacotherapy].

[Article in Russian]

Kovalev GV(1), Shkarupa DD(1), Zaytseva AO(1), Staroseltseva OY(1), Borodulina 
IV(2), Kalinina DS(3), Musienko PE(3)(4)(5)(6).

Author information:
(1)Saint Petersburg State University Hospital. Pirogov Clinic of High Medical 
Technologies, Saint Petersburg, Russia.
(2)Childrens Surgery and Orthopedic Clinic, Department of Non-pulmonary 
Tuberculosis, Institute of Phthisiopulmonology, Ministry of Health of the 
Russian Federation, Saint Petersburg, Russia
(3)Russian Medical Academy of Continuous Postgraduate Education of the Ministry 
of Health of Russia, Moscow, Russian.
(4)Institute of Translational Biomedicine, Saint Petersburg State University, 
Saint Petersburg, Russia.
(5)Russian Research Center of Radiology and Surgical Technologies, Ministry of 
