Advance care planning in patients with advanced cancer: A 6-country, 
cluster-randomised clinical trial.

Korfage IJ(1), Carreras G(2), Arnfeldt Christensen CM(3)(4), Billekens P(5), 
Bramley L(6), Briggs L(7), Bulli F(2), Caswell G(8), Červ B(9), van Delden 
