External beam radiation therapy improves survival in elderly metastatic prostate 
cancer patients with low PSA.

Stolzenbach LF(1), Rosiello G(2), Deuker M(3), Martin T(4), Knipper S(5), Tian 
Z(4), Briganti A(6), Zorn KC(4), Saad F(4), Chun FKH(7), Graefen M(5), 
