Rehabilitation Concerns in the Geriatric Critically Ill and Injured - Part 2.

Nowak B(1), Berry C(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Surgery, Division of Acute Care Surgery, New York University 
Grossman School of Medicine, 550 First Avenue, NBV 12 East 36, New York, NY 
