Low Rates of Preventive Healthcare Service Utilization Among Adolescents and 
Adults With Down Syndrome.

Jensen KM(1), Campagna EJ(2), Juarez-Colunga E(3), Prochazka AV(4), Runyan 
DK(5).

Author information:
(1)Department of Pediatrics, University of Colorado School of Medicine, Aurora, 
Colorado; Department of Internal Medicine, University of Colorado School of 
Medicine, Aurora, Colorado; Adult and Child Consortium for Health Outcomes 
Research and Delivery Science, University of Colorado School of Medicine, 
Aurora, Colorado. Electronic address: kristin.jensen@cuanschutz.edu.
(2)Adult and Child Consortium for Health Outcomes Research and Delivery Science, 
University of Colorado School of Medicine, Aurora, Colorado.
(3)Adult and Child Consortium for Health Outcomes Research and Delivery Science, 
University of Colorado School of Medicine, Aurora, Colorado; University of 
Colorado School of Public Health, Aurora, Colorado.
(4)Department of Internal Medicine, University of Colorado School of Medicine, 
Aurora, Colorado.
(5)Department of Pediatrics, University of Colorado School of Medicine, Aurora, 
